divs: Sighting DetailsI was looking out the bedroom window the blinking lights caught my eye. I thought it was funny a airplane flying that low. The lights were going around like in a circle. It looked like two cylinders with red lights in the middle. It was moving very slow. I did not get exited til I looked at the picture. It disapeared over the mountain. It was traveling SE to SW.
